      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "“Create 24 short, playful starting questions …”\n“First use web search to scan what is unfolding now …”\n“Use current events as trapdoors into durable ideas, not disposable headlines.”\n“Use only the ordered topic history … as signs of curiosity, not evidence of knowledge.”\nMix ~8 history-adjacent + ~8 current + ~8 lateral.\nInput: ISO timestamp + all distinct saved topic labels, oldest→newest.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "“Create 24 short, playful starting questions …”\n“First use web search to scan what is unfolding now …”\n“Use current events as trapdoors into durable ideas, not disposable headlines.”\n“Use only the ordered topic history … as signs of curiosity, not evidence of knowledge.”\nMix ~8 history-adjacent + ~8 current + ~8 lateral.\nInput: ISO timestamp + all distinct saved topic labels, oldest→newest.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
