      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "“Recover evidence for unsupported answer blocks.”\n“Search the web for reliable support, then rewrite only the supplied blocks …”\n“Prefer original or authoritative evidence … Cross-check current, surprising, or contested claims.”\n“Preserve each block number and its role. Do not change any block not supplied.”\nInput: current question + unsupported {block,text} only.\nTools: web_search; max tool calls bounded by unsupported block count.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "“Recover evidence for unsupported answer blocks.”\n“Search the web for reliable support, then rewrite only the supplied blocks …”\n“Prefer original or authoritative evidence … Cross-check current, surprising, or contested claims.”\n“Preserve each block number and its role. Do not change any block not supplied.”\nInput: current question + unsupported {block,text} only.\nTools: web_search; max tool calls bounded by unsupported block count.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
