      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "SPARK\nreasoning: low · max_output_tokens: 4,000\nmax tool calls: 2 · timeout: 25s\n\nSTANDARD\nreasoning: medium · max_output_tokens: 8,000\nmax tool calls: 5 · timeout: 60s\n\nDEEP\nreasoning: high · max_output_tokens: 16,000\nmax tool calls: 10 · timeout: 120s\n\nImportant: max_output_tokens is one shared pool for hidden reasoning, visible JSON, and formatting tokens.",
