      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "GPT-5.6 Sol / Terra / Luna: 1.05M context\nGPT-5.5 and GPT-5.4: 1.05M context\nGPT-5.4 mini / nano: 400K context\nMax model output: 128K\n\nWonderDrive does not set an input-token cap or truncation rule.\nThe compact app-authored prompt is ~1.6K tokens before\ntool/schema overhead. Search results and tool interaction raise\nreported input usage substantially.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GPT-5.6 Sol / Terra / Luna: 1.05M context\nGPT-5.5 and GPT-5.4: 1.05M context\nGPT-5.4 mini / nano: 400K context\nMax model output: 128K\n\nWonderDrive does not set an input-token cap or truncation rule.\nThe compact app-authored prompt is ~1.6K tokens before\ntool/schema overhead. Search results and tool interaction raise\nreported input usage substantially.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
