      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "OPERATION                 CALLS     AVG INPUT     AVG OUTPUT*     AVG REASONING\nLive research                19        28,196          2,556             1,632\nStarter generation           15        13,371            681               233\nCitation recovery             4        14,426            644               360\nCitation repair               7         1,343            304               253\nImage-note repair             5           721            104                84\n\n*output_tokens includes reasoning_tokens. For live research, the approximate non-reasoning remainder averaged 924 tokens.\n\nObserved STANDARD live research used ~32% of its 8K generated-token cap on average; reasoning used ~20% of the cap. A recent nano call used 4,323 / 8,000 generated tokens, including 3,459 reasoning.\n\nThese are local development samples, not guaranteed production distributions.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "OPERATION                 CALLS     AVG INPUT     AVG OUTPUT*     AVG REASONING\nLive research                19        28,196          2,556             1,632\nStarter generation           15        13,371            681               233\nCitation recovery             4        14,426            644               360\nCitation repair               7         1,343            304               253\nImage-note repair             5           721            104                84\n\n*output_tokens includes reasoning_tokens. For live research, the approximate non-reasoning remainder averaged 924 tokens.\n\nObserved STANDARD live research used ~32% of its 8K generated-token cap on average; reasoning used ~20% of the cap. A recent nano call used 4,323 / 8,000 generated tokens, including 3,459 reasoning.\n\nThese are local development samples, not guaranteed production distributions.",
